        "created_at": "2019-03-10T16:33:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>2017 Dauvissat Sechet<br>\nThis nose have I never experienced in a Davissat 1er Cru.<br>\nA lot of fruit and flowery fragrances. No salt\u2026<br>\nAnd the taste lacks totally the briney character of previous vintages. Reminds me more of a Raveneau 1er Cru<br>\nWill the wine change? Lets see over the next decades</p>",
