        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/8797f3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-03-11T15:28:17.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>2015 on Saturday was quite ripe for Sechets.  I guessed a Chassagne Premier from Caillerets or the like.  Partly the vintage I\u2019m sure, but whether it\u2019s part of a stylistic shift that continued in 2017, i don\u2019t know.</p>",
